number_of_successful_pinch_attempts.description: The total number of successful pinches during the activity

hand.description: The hand the activity was performed with

appearance_timestamp.description: The UTC timestamp the ball was displayed

ball_id.description: A unique id to reference a specific appearance of a ball. This integer is incremented for each new ball.

burst_timestamp.description: The timestamp when the burst animation was triggered (in ms since the 1st of January 1970 at midnight UTC)

center_x.description: The x-coordinate of the ball center, the origin being the upward-left corner

center_y.description: The y-coordinate of the ball center, the origin being the upward-left corner

radius_level.description: The id of the interval the radius of the ball was sampled from. (0: 100 to 129; 1: 130 to 159; 2: 160 to 189; 3: 190 to 210 pt)

ball_id.description: The unique id of the ball the user was trying to pinch

first_finger_press_in_timestamp.description: The timestamp when the first finger was pressed in on the screen (beginning of the attempt)

first_finger_press_out_timestamp.description: The press out timestamp of the finger that was pressed in first (null except if the attempt ended because the user lifted the first finger before pressing in the second one)

second_finger_press_in_timestamp.description: The timestamp when the second finger was pressed in on the screen (null if the attempt ended because the user pressed out the first finger)

second_finger_press_out_timestamp.description: The press out timestamp of the finger that was pressed in second (null except if the attempt ended because the user lifted the second finger without triggering the burst animation)

successful.description: Whether the pinch was successful or not. A pinch attempt starts when the user press a first finger on the screen. The attempt ends when the user presses a third finger, or lifts any finger from the screen or if the burst animation is triggered. The attempt is successful if the burst animation is triggered.

timestamp.description: The timestamp of the measurement (in ms since the 1st of January 1970 at midnight UTC)

x.description: The x-axis of the accelerometer in G (G=9.81m/s^2), without gravity (Linear Acceleration)

y.description: The y-axis of the accelerometer in G (G=9.81m/s^2), without gravity (Linear Acceleration)

z.description: The z-axis of the accelerometer in G (G=9.81m/s^2), without gravity (Linear Acceleration)

timestamp.description: The timestamp of the measurement (in ms since the 1st of January 1970 at midnight UTC)

x.description: The unbiased gyration measured on the x-axis of the device in RPS (Radians Per Second)

y.description: The unbiased gyration measured on the y-axis of the device in RPS (Radians Per Second)

z.description: The unbiased gyration measured on the z-axis of the device in RPS (Radians Per Second)

timestamp.description: The timestamp of the measurement (in ms since the 1st of January 1970 at midnight UTC)

x.description: The x-axis of the accelerometer in G (G=9.81m/s^2). Not collected on android versions older than 8.0 Oreo (API 26)

y.description: The y-axis of the accelerometer in G (G=9.81m/s^2). Not collected on android versions older than 8.0 Oreo (API 26)

z.description: The z-axis of the accelerometer in G (G=9.81m/s^2). Not collected on android versions older than 8.0 Oreo (API 26)

timestamp.description: The timestamp of the measurement (in ms since the 1st of January 1970 at midnight UTC)

x.description: The x-axis of the gyroscope in RPS (Radians Per Second)

y.description: The y-axis of the gyroscope in RPS (Radians Per Second)

z.description: The z-axis of the gyroscope in RPS (Radians Per Second)

pressure.description: The touch pressure on the screen

touch_path_id.description: The index of the touch path, representing the index assigned to an individual finger

x.description: The x position of the touch event on the screen

y.description: The y position of the touch event on the screen

number_of_pinch_attempts.description: Sum of pinching attempts per hand

number_of_successful_pinch_attempts.description: Sum of successful pinching attempts per hand

pinching_accuracy.description: Mean of pinching accuracy per hand
